        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>spiced beef</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> with 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil</strong>, and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
