        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dice your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong></p><p>Dice the <strong>remaining red onion </strong>finely</p><p>Add the <strong>diced cucumber</strong> and <strong>diced red onion</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion & cucumber</strong></p>",
