    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, remove the dish from the oven and discard the foil</p><p>Top the<strong> cooked rice </strong>with the<strong> grated cheese </strong>and return it to the oven for a further 5 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>'cheeseburger' rice bake</strong></p>",
