    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>pickling liquid</strong> from the quick pickled onion & cucumber<strong> </strong>to the <strong>sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>discard the remaining liquid</p><p>Mix everything together – this is your <strong>burger sauce</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>diced tomato</strong> with the <strong>drained quick pickled onion & cucumber</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato relish</strong></p>",
